{"tid":202988,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【密室命案】兇案村屋仍然封鎖","createTime":"2017-04-16T02:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T03:02:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c029f26a412f742e358cad75a55513ec53716c70","tid":202988,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:55:28.000Z","msg":"【密室命案】兇案村屋仍然封鎖<br />\n<br />\n元朗田廈路田心村一幢3層高村屋，包租公「平叔」失去聯絡多日，他所居住地下單位傳出惡臭。警方及消防接報到場，發現單位的門窗均反鎖，破門入內發現一名男子倒斃地上，頭部有硬物襲擊傷痕，惟警方未能確定其身份，案件列謀殺處理。<br />\n<br />\n兇案村屋至今仍然封鎖，據街坊陳先生指出，該村屋是以「平叔」的丁權興建，他將丁權出售給發展商，興建期間爛尾，其後由另一發展商完成，過程中涉及借貸，建成後因貸款問題發生金錢糾紛。其後「平叔」在村屋地下一個劏房居住了4、5年，未見有親人來探訪，他喜與村民賭博耍樂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 即Call《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線 ：63836568 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170416&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56570709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170416%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56570709&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSmMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=d18b4dc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170416%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56570709&h=be4615b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170416&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56570709</a>"},{"pid":"7f6321b43946e1e33f41844cc975aacd451a5bd7","tid":202988,"uid":3658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H0c18N8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH0c18N8.jpg&h=ad53c885&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}